node.text:
Summers over . And the money gone . I miss my mama when the tide is low . Moon corrals us to the water and my daddy calls on his favorite daughter for a host of loving words .. I might oblige him . If the money right and the pussy good . Keep it tight for the right one . Save it all for the right one call it perfect timing . (Make it bounce baby do a little more)
I been wiped out like 3 times . Beat dat shit call me nine lives I got perfect timing . Perfect . 
I can’t stop til my shit shine . I can’t stop til I reach my .. perfect 
Tik tok til it go away . Time waits for nary man . I regret all the things we said in haste . Knowing the golden hour waits for me, twilight calls my name . Wrist FROZE let the ice call my name too loud .. double 00’s by name now . 
It’ll all make sense in the end that’s what they say to us . Spending our time smoking angel dust . We on perfect time . Perfect timing . We got it . 
Dir by me . 🦋 danced by @lalanana7 shot by @blaircaldwell edt by @anniebercy

node.text:
Climate change is a HUGE problem . Lots of ppl don’t know it affects communities w Black , Indigenous , and People of Color a lot more than whiter neighborhoods .

Today I'm Super excited to launch the @TAZO Tree Corps!! 🤗 With ur help we'll plant 🌲🌲🌲 in five US cities to fight the effects of climate change. That way we can help EVERYBODY gain access to better air/water , mental health , and lower (!!) utility bills ✨

Go to bit.ly/TAZOTreeCorps and apply before 3/12 !* #TAZOPartner #TAZOTreeCorps

*Applicants for this year’s Tree Corps must be 21+, located in Detroit, Minneapolis, or the San Francisco Bay Area, and interested in working outdoors. Selected applicants will be invited by The Davey Tree Expert Company to participate in a paid training program before transitioning into full-time employment. Check out the full list of requirements at bit.ly/DaveyTreeCorps

node.title: TAZO x SZA launch the TAZO Tree Corps

node.text:
Summers over . And the money gone . I miss my mama when the tide is low . Moon corrals us to the water and my daddy calls on his favorite daughter for a host of loving words .. I might oblige him . If the money right and the pussy good . Keep it tight for the right one . Save it all for the right one call it perfect timing . (Make it bounce baby do a little more)
I been wiped out like 3 times . Beat dat shit call me nine lives I got perfect timing . Perfect . 
I can’t stop til my shit shine . I can’t stop til I reach my .. perfect 
Tik tok til it go away . Time waits for nary man . I regret all the things we said in haste . Knowing the golden hour waits for me, twilight calls my name . Wrist FROZE let the ice call my name too loud .. double 00’s by name now . 
It’ll all make sense in the end that’s what they say to us . Spending our time smoking angel dust . We on perfect time . Perfect timing . We got it . 
Dir by me . 🦋 danced by @lalanana7 shot by @blaircaldwell edt by @anniebercy
